      "duplicate non-null sales_ticket_issue_id is accepted",
      "revoked/refunded Sales-origin attendee remains scanner-acceptable",
      "Tickera-origin regression behavior is untested",
      "an Ash Attendee resource is created",
      "ticket issuance or provider logic appears in the slice"
    ],
    "green_requires": [
      "Sales-origin attendees survive Tickera reconciliation",
      "Tickera-origin attendees still reconcile normally",
      "Sales linkage/scanner eligibility fields are preserved",
      "duplicate non-null sales_ticket_issue_id is rejected if used",
      "revoked/refunded/cancelled Sales-origin attendees are scanner-non-acceptable",
      "no Ash migration of Attendees and no provider/ticket issuance behavior"
